abicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011000, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah by Your knowledge of the unseen and Your power over creation give me life so long as You know that life is good for me and make me die when death is good for me. O Allah, I ask You (to help me attain) sincere speech and fear of You in pleasure and in anger and moderation in wealth and in poverty.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Parwardigaar! Tu ghaiyb se bhi waaqif hai aur tamaam maujoodaat par qaadir o tawaana hai. Mujhe us waqt tak zindah rakh jab tak zindagi mere liye mufeed (khair) hai aur mujhe us waqt maut de jab khair o neyki ko meri maut mein dekhe. Khudawanda! Khushi o ghami mein ikhlaas aur Tujh se darte rehne aur faqr o sarwat-mandi se mayaana-rawi (moderate) ki khwaastga ho aur Tujh se aisi ne’mat maangti hu jo khatm na ho aur Tujh se aisi cheez ki talab-gaar hu jo mujhe khush kare aur khatm na ho.", "Urdu": "پروردگارا!آپ غیب سے بھی واقف ہیں اور تمام موجودات پر قادر و توانا۔ مجھے اس وقت تک زندہ رکھ جب تک زندگی میرے لئے مفید ہے اور مجھے اس وقت موت دے جب خیرو نیکی کو میری موت میں دیکھے۔ خداوند! خوشی و غمی میں اخلاص اور تجھ سے ڈرتے رہنے اور فقر و ثروت مندی سے میانہ روی کی خواستگاہوں اور تجھ سے ایسی نعمت مانگتی ہوں جو ختم نہ ہو۔ اور تم سے ایسی چیز کی طلبگار ہوں جو مجھے خوش کرے اور ختم نہ ہو۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA BE-I’LMEKAL GHAYBE, WA QUDRATEKA A’LAL KHALQE, AHYENEE MAA A’LIMTAL HAYAATA KHAYRAN LEE, WA TAWAFFANEE EZAA KAANATIL WAFAA-TO KHAYRAN LEE. ALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA KALEMATAL IKHLAASE, WA KHASYATAKA FIR REZAA WAL GHAZABE, WAL QASDA FIL GHENAA WAL FAQRE, WA AS-ALOKA NA-E’EMAN LAA YANFADO, WA AS-ALOKA QURRATA A’YNIN LAA TANQATE-O’.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ بِعِلْمِکَ الْغَیْبِ وَقُدْرَتِکَ عَلَی الْخَلْقِ، اَحْیِنِیْ مَا عَلِمْتَ الْحَیَاۃَ خَیْرًا لِی، وَتَوَفَّنِیْ اِذَا کَانَتِ الْوَفَاۃُ خَیْرًا لِیْ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْئَلُکَ کَلِمَۃَ الْاِخْلَاصِ، وَخَشْیَتَکَ فِی الرِّضَا وَالْغَضَبِ، وَالْقَصْدَ فِی الْغِنٰی وَالْفَقْرِ وَاَسْئَلُکَ نَعِیْمًا لَا یَنْفَدُ، وَاَسْئَلُکَ قُرَّۃَ عَیْنٍ لَا تَنْقَطِعُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011001, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "And I ask You for favors that will not end for delight of the eyes that will not be cut off for satisfaction with the Decree for ease after death for Your sight, and the desire to meet You without any harmful affliction nor any dark trial. O Allah adorn us with the adornment of faith and make us guides who are guided, O Lord of the worlds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Allah! Mai Teri baargah mein dua karti hu keh is dunya mein Teri raza par raazi rehne ki taufiq inaayat farma aur marne ke baad achchhi zindagi ataa farma aur mulaqaat ke shaidaaiy ko apna deedaar naseeb farma. Aisa deedaar jis mein kisi qism ka ranj o alam na ho. Ay Parwardiqaar! Hamein imaan ki zeenat se mazeen farma aur hamein hidaayat dene waala qaraar de aur sahih hidaayat karne waala qaraar de ta-keh Teri hidaayat hamare shaamil'e haal ho, ay dono jahan ke Paalne waale.", "Urdu": "اے اللہ میں تیری بارگاہ میں دعا کرتی ہوں کہ اس دنیا میں تیری رضا پر راضی رہنے کی توفیق عنایت فرما اور مرنے کے بعد اجھی زندگی عطا فرما اور ملاقات کے شیدائی کو اپنا دیدار نصیب فرما۔ ایسا دیدار جس میں کسی قسم کا رنج و الم نہ ہو۔ اے پروردگارا!ہمیں ایمان کی زینت سے مزین فرما اور ہمیں ہدایت دینے والا قرار دے اور صحیح ہدایت کرنے والا قرار دے تاکہ تیری ہدایت ہمارے شامل حال ہو۔ اے دونوں جہاں کے پالنے والے۔", "RArabic": "WA AS-ALOKAR REZAA BIL-QAZAA-E, WA AS-ALOKA BARDAL A’YSHE BA’DAL MAWTE, WA AS-ALOKAN NAZARA ELAA WAJHEKA WASH SHAWQA ELAA LEQAA-EKA MIN GHAYRE ZARRAA-A MOZIRRATIN, WA LAA FITNATIN MUZLEMATIN, ALLAAHUMMA ZAYYINNAA BE-ZEENATIL EEMAANE WAJ A’LNAA HODAATAN MAHDIYYEENA YAA RABBAL A’ALAMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَسْئَلُکَ الرِّضَا بِالْقَضَاۗئِ، وَاَسْئَلُکَ بَرْدَ الْعَیْشِ بَعْدَ الْمَوْتِ، وَاَسْئَلُکَ النَّظَرَ اِلٰی وَجْہِکَ، وَالشَّوْقَ اِلٰی لِقَاۗئِکَ مِنْ غَیْرِ ضَرَّاۗئٍ مُضِرَّۃٍ وَلَا فِتْنَۃٍ مُّظْلِمَۃٍ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ زَیِّنَّا بِزِیْنَۃِ الْاِیْمَانِ، وَاجْعَلْنَا ہُدَاۃً مَہْدِیِّیْنَ، یَا رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "A